title: TB Karen Torments Harry Again | AHS: Double Feature - Episode 2: "Pale" (HQ Clip)
author: AHS Crave
comment: TB Karen is one of my favorite AHS characters in the entire series. She keeps this up she might be my favorite. 😂
I've got a feeling TB Karen will be yet another iconic AHS character played by the one and only Sarah Paulson.  I'm no fortune teller, but I can see it already.  Sarah Paulson rules Supreme!
The shade that grocer threw asking how the  writing was going.
In all of her craziness, there is such an innocence. Def one of the best characters.
"What were you Thursteyyy ?!" Alwaysss gets mee haha 🤣
